爱心…… </div><div class="t m0 x1c hc y1a5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">当然，<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls21">我们更应该把心放在当下，<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls0">专注于现在要做的事，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y1a6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">专注于此生要做的事，<span class="_ _a"></span>特别是今晚的演讲。<span class="_ _a"></span>从当下的点滴做</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y1a7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">起，会帮助我们有效减少造成这些暴力的因素。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c hc y1a8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">今晚，<span class="_ _8"></span>很荣幸邀请到索达吉堪布。<span class="_ _8"></span>担任今晚翻译的，<span class="_ _8"></span>是</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y1a9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">哈佛的在读博士生宁扎多吉。<span class="_ _a"></span>他跟随范德康教授学习，<span class="_ _a"></span>可能</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y1aa ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">在座很多人也很熟悉。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
